<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Copperfield</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">In the north of Copperfield Park is the community hall, complete with wheelchair access, meeting rooms, a sound system and an indoor fireplace.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">North of Copperfield is <a href="/mckenzie-towne.php">McKenzie Towne</a>, which has a small commercial district, characterizing a typical Main Street one would find in any small town. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located on High Street, the area has a pharmacy, restaurants, cafes, grocery store and a pub, bringing many needs closer to home. For those looking for more retail, you’ll find what you’re looking for along 130th avenue. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The street is lined with restaurants, big box stores, pharmacies, and various other retail and miscellaneous shops for people to explore.</p>
        </div>
